description.narrative: This activity (Short Term Independent Technical Experts) is a component of Punjab Economic Opportunities Programme (PEOP) reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £341,205. This component benefits Pakistan, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Research/scientific institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited, Mott MacDonald Limited. The start date is 01-01-2011 and the end date is 31-10-2015.
